<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">
Eleven new species were described (
<bibRefCitation author="Han, Hongxiang" journalOrPublisher="Entomological Science" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" pagination="382 - 410" refId="B5535919" refString="Han, Hongxiang, Xue, Dayong, 2009. Taxonomic review of Hemistola Warren, 1893 from China, with descriptions of seven new species (Lepidoptera: Geometridae, Geometrinae). Entomological Science 12 (4): 382 - 410" title="Taxonomic review of Hemistola Warren, 1893 from China, with descriptions of seven new species (Lepidoptera: Geometridae, Geometrinae)" volume="12" year="2009">Han and Xue 2009</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Chang, W-C" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" pagination="538 - 550" refId="B5535782" refString="Chang, W-C, Wu, S, 2013. Review of the genus Hemistola Warren, 1893 in Taiwan with notes on an unusual conifer-feeding larva and descriptions of three new species (Lepidoptera, Geometridae, Geometrinae). Zootaxa 3741 (4): 538 - 550" title="Review of the genus Hemistola Warren, 1893 in Taiwan with notes on an unusual conifer-feeding larva and descriptions of three new species (Lepidoptera, Geometridae, Geometrinae)" volume="3741" year="2013">Chang and Wu 2013</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Wu, S" journalOrPublisher="Tinea" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" pagination="6 - 9" refId="B5537268" refString="Wu, S, 2019. Description of a new species of Hemistola Warren, 1893 from China (Geometridae: Geometrinae). Tinea 25: 6 - 9" title="Description of a new species of Hemistola Warren, 1893 from China (Geometridae: Geometrinae)." volume="25" year="2019">Wu 2019</bibRefCitation>
). The species 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Hemistola" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hemistola flavitincta" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavitincta">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Hemistola flavitincta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Hemistola" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hemistola liliana" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="liliana">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Hemistola liliana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were transferred to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Swinhoe" authorityYear="1893" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Herochroma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Herochroma" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Herochroma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Swinhoe, 1893 by 
<bibRefCitation author="Parsons, MS" journalOrPublisher="CSIRO, Clayton North, Victoria, Australia" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" refId="B5536979" refString="Parsons, MS, Scoble, MJ, Honey, MR, Pitkin, LM, Pitkin, BR, 1999. Geometrid moths of the world: a catalogue (Lepidoptera, Geometridae). CSIRO, Clayton North, Victoria, Australia" title="Geometrid moths of the world: a catalogue (Lepidoptera, Geometridae)." year="1999">Parsons et al. (1999)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Pitkin, L" journalOrPublisher="Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" pagination="343 - 412" refId="B5536999" refString="Pitkin, L, Han, H, James, S, 2007. Moths of the tribe Pseudoterpnini (Geometridae: Geometrinae): a review of the genera. Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society 150 (2): 343 - 412" title="Moths of the tribe Pseudoterpnini (Geometridae: Geometrinae): a review of the genera" volume="150" year="2007">Pitkin et al. (2007)</bibRefCitation>
implied this was an editorial error and, citing a complete absence of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Swinhoe" authorityYear="1893" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Herochroma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Herochroma" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Herochroma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
diagnostic characters, transferred both species back to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Warren" authorityYear="1893" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Hemistola" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hemistola" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Hemistola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
